"""
Hand Gesture Recognition System - Multi-Stream ST-GCN with Mixture of Experts
==============================================================================
A comprehensive deep learning system for recognizing 13 hand gesture classes from
3D landmark sequences. The architecture combines spatial-temporal graph convolutions
(ST-GCN) for processing hand skeleton data with Transformer networks for engineered
features, all integrated through a Mixture of Experts (MoE) classification head.

Key Features:
- Multi-stream processing: raw landmarks, normalized, differences, and engineered features
- Advanced data augmentation: rotation, time warping, frame dropout, translation, noise
- Class-balanced augmentation to target_count samples per class
- 5-fold cross-validation with ensemble inference
- Test-Time Augmentation (TTA) for robust predictions
"""

